{"title":"Java 與 Kotlin 對照筆記","uid":"ec689fac42391847d1970b8ad306d112","slug":"java-kotlin-comparison-notes","date":"2022-12-21T04:00:50.000Z","updated":"2023-01-31T03:45:13.458Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/java-kotlin-comparison-notes.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.imgur.com/dkq1jBA.jpg","content":"<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dkq1jBA.jpg\" alt=\"cover\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"存取修飾子\"><a href=\"#存取修飾子\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"存取修飾子\"></a>存取修飾子</h1><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>修飾子 <br> Access Modifiers</th>\n<th>Java</th>\n<th>Kotlin</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><code>public</code></td>\n<td>所有類可存取 <br> All classes can be accessed</td>\n<td>所有類可存取 <strong>（預設）</strong> <br> All classes can be accessed <strong>(default)</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>private</code></td>\n<td>當前類可存取 <br> Only the current class can be accessed</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>protected</code></td>\n<td>當前類、子類、同一套件路徑下的類可存取 <br> Only the current class, sub-class and the classes that belong to the same package can be accessed</td>\n<td>當前類、子類可存取 <br> Only the current class, sub-class can be accessed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>default</code></td>\n<td>同一套件路徑下的類可存取 <strong>（預設）</strong> <br> Only the classes that belong to the same package can be accessed <strong>(default)</strong></td>\n<td>無 <br> None</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>internal</code></td>\n<td>無 <br> None</td>\n<td>同一模組中的類可存取 <br> Only the class that is inside the same module can be accessed</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"決策邏輯\"><a href=\"#決策邏輯\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"決策邏輯\"></a>決策邏輯</h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"選擇邏輯-if-else\"><a href=\"#選擇邏輯-if-else\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"選擇邏輯 - if else\"></a>選擇邏輯 - if else</h2><details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>隱藏內容</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Java</span></div><code class=\"language-java\">if (x &gt; y) z &#x3D; x;\nelse z &#x3D; y;</code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</details>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-kotlin\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Kotlin</span></div><code class=\"language-kotlin\">z &#x3D; if (x &gt; y) x else y</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"情況邏輯-switch-case\"><a href=\"#情況邏輯-switch-case\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"情況邏輯 - switch case\"></a>情況邏輯 - switch case</h2><details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>隱藏內容</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Java</span></div><code class=\"language-java\">switch (score) &#123;\n    case 10:\n    case 9:\n        grade &#x3D; &quot;Excellent&quot;;\n\t    break;\n    case 8:\n    case 7:\n    case 6:\n        grade &#x3D; &quot;Good&quot;;\n        break;\n    case 5:\n    case 4:\n        grade &#x3D; &quot;OK&quot;;\n        break;\n    case 3:\n    case 2:\n    case 1:\n    default:\n        grade &#x3D; &quot;Fail&quot;;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</details>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-kotlin\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Kotlin</span></div><code class=\"language-kotlin\">var grade &#x3D; when (score) &#123;\n    9, 10 -&gt; &quot;Excellent&quot;\n    in 6..8 -&gt; &quot;Good&quot;\n    4, 5 -&gt; &quot;OK&quot;\n    else -&gt; &quot;Fail&quot;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"迴圈\"><a href=\"#迴圈\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"迴圈\"></a>迴圈</h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"For-迴圈\"><a href=\"#For-迴圈\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"For 迴圈\"></a>For 迴圈</h2><details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>隱藏內容</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Java</span></div><code class=\"language-java\">for (int i &#x3D; 1; i &lt;&#x3D; 10 ; i++) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor (int i &#x3D; 1; i &lt; 10 ; i++) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor (int i &#x3D; 10; i &gt;&#x3D; 0 ; i--) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor (int i &#x3D; 1; i &lt;&#x3D; 10 ; i+&#x3D;2) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor (int i &#x3D; 10; i &gt;&#x3D; 0 ; i-&#x3D;2) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor (String item : collection) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor (Map.Entry&lt;String, String&gt; entry: map.entrySet()) &#123;&#125;</code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</details>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-kotlin\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Kotlin</span></div><code class=\"language-kotlin\">for (i in 1..10) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor (i in 1 until 10) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor (i in 10 downTo 0) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor (i in 1..10 step 2) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor (i in 10 downTo 0 step 2) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor (item in collection) &#123;&#125;\n\nfor ((key, value) in map) &#123;&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"變異子與存取子-x2F-數據類\"><a href=\"#變異子與存取子-x2F-數據類\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"變異子與存取子 &#x2F; 數據類\"></a>變異子與存取子 &#x2F; 數據類</h1><p>要是實現數據類的話，我高度建議使用 Kotlin 語法的數據類結構 <code>data class</code> ，因為它<strong>簡化並內置了</strong> Java 數據類的 <code>getXXX()</code>、<code>setXXX()</code>、<code>toString()</code>、<code>hashCode()</code> 等方法。</p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>隱藏內容</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Java</span></div><code class=\"language-java\">public class Person &#123;\n    private String name;\n    private int age;\n\n    public Person(String name) &#123;\n        this.name &#x3D; name;\n    &#125;\n\n    public void setName(String name) &#123;\n        this.name &#x3D; name;\n    &#125;\n\n    public String getName() &#123;\n        return name;\n    &#125;\n\n    public void setAge(int age) &#123;\n        this.age &#x3D; age;\n    &#125;\n\n    public String getAge() &#123;\n        return age;\n    &#125;\n&#125;\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; to use\nPerson person &#x3D; new Person(&quot;Steve&quot;);\nSystem.out.println(person.getName());</code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</details>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-kotlin\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Kotlin</span></div><code class=\"language-kotlin\">data class Person(\n    val name: String,\n    val age: Int\n)\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; to use\nval person &#x3D; Person(&quot;Steve&quot;)\nprintln(person.name)</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"高階函數\"><a href=\"#高階函數\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"高階函數\"></a>高階函數</h1><details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>隱藏內容</summary>\n<p><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Java 沒有這個所謂的高階函數。</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public void saySomething() &#123;\n    System.out.println(&quot;Hello World&quot;);\n&#125;\npublic boolean isACoolFeature() &#123;\n    return true;\n&#125;\npublic int getNum() &#123;\n    return 10;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</details>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-kotlin\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Kotlin</span></div><code class=\"language-kotlin\">fun saySomething() &#x3D; println(&quot;Hello World&quot;);\nfun isACoolFeature() &#x3D; true;\nfun getNum() &#x3D; 10;</code></pre>","text":" 修飾子 Access Modifiers Java Kotlin 所有類可存取 All classes can be accessed 所有類可存取 （預設） All classes can be accessed (default) 當前類可存取 Only the curre...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.2k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":12,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Kotlin","slug":"Kotlin","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Kotlin.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%98%E5%8F%96%E4%BF%AE%E9%A3%BE%E5%AD%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">存取修飾子</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B1%BA%E7%AD%96%E9%82%8F%E8%BC%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">決策邏輯</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87%E9%82%8F%E8%BC%AF-if-else\"><span class=\"toc-text\">選擇邏輯 - if else</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E9%82%8F%E8%BC%AF-switch-case\"><span class=\"toc-text\">情況邏輯 - switch case</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BF%B4%E5%9C%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">迴圈</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#For-%E8%BF%B4%E5%9C%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">For 迴圈</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%8A%E7%95%B0%E5%AD%90%E8%88%87%E5%AD%98%E5%8F%96%E5%AD%90-x2F-%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E9%A1%9E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">變異子與存取子 &#x2F; 數據類</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%AB%98%E9%9A%8E%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">高階函數</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.ibb.co/zRvn96K/20210718-233824.jpg","link":"/","description":"Everything is possible, as long as you are powerful.","socials":{"github":"http://bit.ly/3WWvvfn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"youtube":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-youtube","link":"https://bit.ly/3C9RlUL"},"facebook":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-facebook","link":null},"instagram":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-instagram","link":null}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"利用 Hexo 建立 GitHub 寄存網誌","uid":"a990d8c2eefbb26d914d318577aa9256","slug":"hexo-create-blog","date":"2022-12-23T23:53:52.000Z","updated":"2023-01-28T03:46:15.063Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo-create-blog.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.imgur.com/WlMrWct.jpg","text":" 大家好，歡迎來到我的網誌。欸。。？這裏為什麼好像。。整個樣子都不一樣啊。。 對啦，因為我「搬家」了。 為什麼我要由 Google Blogspot 轉用 Hexo？因為 Blogspot 在加載網誌實在太慢了！！！！有時還要跑不起來。。。於是就改用 Hexo 建立網誌了，安裝方...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"5.8k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"網頁開發","slug":"網頁開發","count":9,"path":"api/categories/網頁開發.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"終端機指令","slug":"終端機指令","count":7,"path":"api/tags/終端機指令.json"}],"author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.ibb.co/zRvn96K/20210718-233824.jpg","link":"/","description":"Everything is possible, as long as you are powerful.","socials":{"github":"http://bit.ly/3WWvvfn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn